[SN]TITLE[SN]
M8 closed after major crash at Charing Cross in Glasgow

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The westbound M8 motorway has been closed in central Glasgow following a serious crash.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
At least five vehicles are believed to have been involved in the collision at J18 Charing Cross.
Emergency services are at the scene and traffic is being directed off at J17, down Newton St and back on at J19, before the Kingston Bridge.
